== Install RVM ==
$ bash -s stable < <(curl -s https://raw.github.com/wayneeseguin/rvm/master/binscripts/rvm-installer)
$ source ~/.bash_profile

== Install ruby ==
$ sudo apt-get install sqlite3-dev
$ rvm install 1.9.2
$ rvm use 1.9.2

== Get the code ==
$ git clone git://github.com/noacta/noacta.git
$ cd noacta
$ bundle install --without production
$ rake run

